      "description": "Three mesh refinement levels (coarse 2.1M, medium 5.8M, fine 14.2M cells) were evaluated at the 4 L/min / 2500 RPM operating point. The Grid Convergence Index for the volume-averaged scalar stress was 1.8%, confirming discretization error is within acceptable bounds for MRL 2.",
      "passFailStatus": "Pass",
