    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The CFD model predicts relative hemolysis index values below the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five target operating points, with a mean absolute error of 0.07 against the multi-centre registry dataset. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 for MRL 2. The assessment team judged the totality of evidence sufficient to support the intended use decision for the Class II CPB device.",
